{"tid":1927442,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知咩標題","createTime":"2020-03-15T18:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T18:57:43.000Z","uid":313383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"305e8565daefab9b792c5e6938a9ed52c7df268a","tid":1927442,"uid":313383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:51:44.000Z","msg":"每次見到男朋友電話彈出哥個女仔覆既wts就好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（佢地係同學）<br />\nwts內容都係問下project 但每隔兩三日就傾一次<br />\n呢排因爲武肺 唔洗返學 反而佢地仲多左傾計<br />\n但男朋友平時好少同我WhatsApp 傾計 搵佢佢多數都係Hea覆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男朋友之前亦都試過因爲哥個女仔講大話呃過我幾次  <br />\n同過佢講過我介意 但換泥既係佢開始會暪住我 因為知我介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家見到佢在線上唔係覆我 都會覺得佢係同個女仔傾緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我問題諗多左定佢問題 唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5a0d9a6ab50c08f3ec1bf0a2c88e877d42af92","tid":1927442,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"私了個女仔"}]}